&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After an unexpected detour to Austin for a non specified fuel problem, my flight arrived in Dallas yesterday evening at a little past seven pm. Im here, Im safe, Im with the family , furry and non furry alike. I'll probably post some more over the weekend but for now Im going to sit down in the couch at Chez Cliff with my cup of coffee and my current book. 

Currently Reading FaeFever by Karen Marie Moning 

&quot; Electric. Wild. One foot in the swamp. Never going to crawl all the way out. And I&nbsp;wanted to have sex with whatever he was.&quot;&nbsp;

In early May I&nbsp;made my ten year anniversary with the company I work for.&nbsp; In recognition of that, the company I work for gave the ten year employees a clock , mine went back because they misspelled my name on in, a ten year pin and a CRUISE&nbsp;!!!!!!!!!!!!&nbsp;It's all paid for. 
I dont know the details yet as far as how long it is and where to but, we are going on FREE CRUISE&nbsp;!!!!!!&nbsp; 

Oh I&nbsp;cant wait to start planning this !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!&nbsp;


Cruise Ship Puppy!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!&nbsp;

Tomorrow morning at nine AM I&nbsp;have orientation at school. OMG school!!!&nbsp;I have some final paperwork to bring to the school and then I&nbsp;have to make some phone calls. Tomorrow I sceduele my classes. It wont let me sceduele online for whatever reason it says im not eligible. Maybe because Im&nbsp; a first time student. Im excited and terrified all the same and im not even starting actual classes until next month. If I figured everything out right, I will have class Monday Tuesday and Wednesday evenings... This leaves Thursday-Sunday evenings open. I&nbsp;think I&nbsp;can do this. What it will mean is changing my WW night. I may&nbsp; have to start going on Thursday evenings. Must make sacrifice for school. Its going to take a long time but I can do this, I HAVE to do this. I&nbsp;WILL&nbsp;do this. 

Look out y'all. Im gonna haz me an education. 

Ferocious, Bloodthirsty, and EDUCATED leatherwoman!!!!!&nbsp;
